                betul: 'IAM Access Analyzer вҖ” direka khusus kenal pasti resource yang dikongsi dengan entiti luar zone of trust (public/cross-account/cross-Org), guna automated reasoning. Keyword "identify resources shared/exposed to external/public/other accounts" вҶ’ IAM Access Analyzer, BUKAN Config, BUKAN GuardDuty (itu threat aktif).',
