              caption: '"Who deleted / audit log of API calls" вҶ’ CloudTrail. "Alarm bila CPU > 80%, monitor logs" вҶ’ CloudWatch. "Is this resource compliant, what changed over time, config drift" вҶ’ AWS Config.',
