                takeaway: 'Keyword "rarely accessed / long-term / 90+ days / compliance archive" вҶ’ Archive tier (jimat sampai 75% TAPI restore lambat 24-72 jam + min 90 hari). Backup yang mungkin kena restore cepat вҶ’ kekal Standard tier.',
