                takeaway: 'Snapshot = backup 1 volume. AMI = blueprint untuk boot EC2 (mengandungi snapshot). Recycle Bin = jaring keselamatan bila tersilap padam. Keyword "accidentally deleted snapshot / protect against deletion" вҶ’ Recycle Bin.',
