            sifir: ["Outposts = rack/server hardware AWS DALAM data center kau (on-prem), API AWS sama", "2 form factor: rack 42U (penuh) В· server 1U/2U (kecik, single server)", "Run EC2, EBS, RDS, ECS, EKS, S3 on Outposts вҖ” data kekal on-prem", "Use case: data residency/compliance, ultra-low latency ke sistem on-prem, local processing, consistent hybrid", "Service Link = control plane balik ke parent Region; Local Gateway (LGW) = trafik on-prem (racks)", "Outposts вү  data transfer (itu DataSync/Snow) ; вү  hybrid storage je (itu Storage Gateway) ; вү  AWS-owned metro infra (itu Local Zones)"],
