              takeaway: 'User Data = RUN script (verb). Metadata = BACA info (noun). "bootstrap / auto-install on launch" вҶ’ User Data; "retrieve instance ID / IAM role credentials from inside" вҶ’ Metadata. Dua-dua guna 169.254.169.254 tapi path beza (user-data vs meta-data).',
