                caption: 'Tanya profil I/O dulu. Random I/O вҶ’ SSD (gp3 default, io2 kritikal + satu-satunya Multi-Attach). Sequential вҶ’ HDD (st1 kerap-akses, sc1 cold). INGAT exam: "highest IOPS / Multi-Attach" вҶ’ io2 В· "cost-effective default / boot" вҶ’ gp3 В· "big data / log sequential" вҶ’ st1 В· "lowest cost / infrequent" вҶ’ sc1.',
