                caption: 'INGAT exam: IOPS = kira BILANGAN operasi kecil (tol: berapa kereta lalu) вҶ’ random вҶ’ SSD. Throughput = kira ISIPADU data (lori: berapa tan barang) вҶ’ sequential вҶ’ HDD. Soalan sebut "high IOPS / random / database" вҶ’ SSD; "high throughput / sequential / log / big data" вҶ’ HDD.',
