              'Magnetic (standard) = LEGACY/previous-gen (~100 IOPS). Jangan pilih untuk sistem moden; AWS sendiri tak galak. Kadang jadi umpan "cheapest" вҖ” current-gen cheapest sebenarnya sc1.',
              'PRICING (us-east-1): gp3 $0.08/GB-mo (base, includes 3K IOPS + 125 MB/s) В· io2 $0.125/GB-mo + $0.065/provisioned-IOPS-mo (paling mahal) В· io1 sama family В· st1 $0.045/GB-mo В· sc1 $0.015/GB-mo (cheapest current-gen). Exam: "cheapest EBS" вҶ’ sc1; "mission-critical DB" вҶ’ io2.',
