              'RESTORE job: Glacier Flexible & Deep Archive BUKAN direct GET вҖ” kena initiate restore job dulu (Flexible: Expedited 1-5min / Standard 3-5hr / Bulk 5-12hr; Deep Archive: Standard ~12hr / Bulk ~48hr, NO Expedited). Glacier Instant tak perlu restore (GET terus ms).',
