            detailsLabel: 'Routing Policies',
            storageDetails: 'Simple вҶ’ 1 resource, no health check, no failover\nWeighted вҶ’ split traffic by % (A=70%, B=30%)\nLatency-based вҶ’ route to lowest latency AWS region\nFailover вҶ’ primary (active) + secondary (passive) via health check\nGeolocation вҶ’ route by user\'s country/continent\nGeoproximity вҶ’ route by geographic distance + bias\nMulti-Value вҶ’ up to 8 healthy records, random selection',
