              caption: 'Jangan keliru Latency vs Geolocation: Latency = paling LAJU (performance, region terbaik network); Geolocation = ikut NEGARA user (compliance/bahasa) walaupun bukan paling laju. INGAT exam: "fastest/lowest latency" вҶ’ Latency-based; "by country/comply/serve language" вҶ’ Geolocation; "active-passive DR" вҶ’ Failover.',
