              'Order penting / no duplicate вҶ’ FIFO (.fifo, 300/s atau 3000 batch)',
              'Visibility Timeout < masa proses вҶ’ mesej muncul balik вҶ’ DUPLICATE. Naikkan timeout',
              'Cross-account hantar ke queue вҶ’ SQS queue policy (resource-based), bukan IAM je',
              'Long polling (WaitTime>0, max 20s) вҶ’ kurangkan empty response & kos API',
              'DLQ = SQS queue asing untuk mesej gagal. Cetus bila ReceiveCount > maxReceiveCount',
              'Poison pill (data corrupt) вҶ’ DLQ, kalau tak server pusing proses sampai bil melambung',
              'DLQ source FIFO вҶ’ DLQ kena FIFO juga; source Standard вҶ’ DLQ kena Standard',
