                umpan: 'A (Read Replica) paling menipu вҖ” nampak "scaling RDS" terus pilih. TAPI Read Replica scale READ je (offload SELECT); ia LANGSUNG tak bantu WRITE вҖ” malah write kena replicate ke replica juga. C (upgrade instance) = vertical scaling, dah dikecualikan (bajet). D (DynamoDB) = re-architecture besar, mahal & berisiko untuk relational e-commerce, bukan "cost-effective minimal change".',
                betul: 'B вҖ” SQS di depan RDS (queue-based load leveling): app campak write request masuk queue, consumer proses ke RDS ikut kadar yang RDS MAMPU. Lonjakan write diserap dalam queue (buffer) вҶ’ RDS tak kena hentam lebih IOPS limit. Murah (SQS sen je) + tak perlu vertical scaling. Keyword "write-heavy spike / nearing IOPS limit / cost-effective / no vertical scaling" вҶ’ SQS buffer writes (queue-based load leveling). INGAT: Read Replica = READ scaling, BUKAN write.',
