              'IAM policy dalam target account SAHAJA tidak cukup untuk cross-account SQS access. Queue policy mesti explicitly allow source account principal',
              'Exam: "allow another AWS account to send messages to SQS queue" вҶ’ SQS queue policy (resource-based)',
              'Long Polling (ReceiveMessageWaitTimeSeconds > 0, max 20s): consumer WAITS for message before returning. Reduces empty responses + API call costs. Short polling = returns immediately even if empty.',
              'Visibility Timeout: message hidden from OTHER consumers after retrieved. If processing takes longer than timeout вҶ’ message becomes visible again вҶ’ DUPLICATE processing. Fix: increase timeout to exceed max processing time, or use ChangeMessageVisibility mid-processing.',
