            sebabApa: "Amazon MQ wujud sebab banyak app lama (on-prem) dah guna ActiveMQ/RabbitMQ dengan protokol standard (AMQP, MQTT, STOMP, JMS). Kalau nak migrate ke AWS dan tukar ke SQS/SNS = kena rewrite code (API AWS proprietary). Amazon MQ = managed broker yang cakap protokol standard tu, jadi app lama boleh lift-and-shift tanpa ubah code. Ia 'jambatan' untuk legacy, bukan pilihan default.",
            sifir: ["Amazon MQ = MIGRATION/legacy; SQS+SNS = cloud-native app BARU", "Support protokol terbuka: AMQP, MQTT, STOMP, OpenWire, JMS, WebSocket", "2 engine: ActiveMQ (banyak protokol) В· RabbitMQ (AMQP terutamanya)", "App guna MQTT/STOMP вҶ’ mesti engine ActiveMQ", "Managed BROKER (instance), bukan serverless macam SQS вҖ” skala terhad ikut saiz broker", "Deployment: single-instance (dev) В· active/standby multi-AZ (prod HA, guna EFS)"],
            perangkap: [{"soalan": "On-prem app guna ActiveMQ (AMQP), nak migrate ke AWS TANPA ubah code. Service mana?", "umpan": "SQS + SNS вҖ” sangka 'messaging di AWS mesti SQS/SNS'.", "betul": "Amazon MQ. SQS/SNS guna API proprietary вҶ’ kena rewrite code. MQ support protokol standard untuk lift-and-shift. Keyword: 'migrate existing' + 'AMQP/MQTT' + 'no code change'."}, {"soalan": "Bina app messaging cloud-native BARU, perlu auto-scale hampir tanpa had. Amazon MQ?", "umpan": "Amazon MQ вҖ” sangka ia general-purpose messaging untuk semua.", "betul": "SQS + SNS. MQ = broker instance (skala terhad, mahal sikit). App baru вҶ’ SQS/SNS serverless. Keyword: 'new app' + 'scale' вҶ’ SQS/SNS, BUKAN MQ."}],
            detailsLabel: 'Amazon MQ вҖ” komponen utama',
            storageDetails: 'Engine вҶ’ ActiveMQ atau RabbitMQ (pilih ikut protokol app sedia ada)\nProtokol terbuka вҶ’ AMQP, MQTT, STOMP, OpenWire, WebSocket, JMS вҖ” sebab itu app lama boleh sambung tanpa tukar code\nBroker вҶ’ instance yang AWS urus (patching, HA). Bukan serverless macam SQS\nDeployment вҶ’ single-instance (dev/test) atau active/standby multi-AZ (production HA, auto-failover guna EFS)\nQueue & Topic вҶ’ satu broker boleh ada queues (point-to-point) DAN topics (pub/sub) sekali',
            scenario: '"Company ada on-premises app guna ActiveMQ, nak migrate ke AWS tanpa tukar code" вҶ’ Amazon MQ. App baru? вҶ’ guna SQS/SNS (simpler, cheaper, cloud-native). Amazon MQ = MIGRATION/LEGACY. SQS = cloud-native new apps.',
