              'Stack Policy: JSON policy yang lindungi resource kritikal (e.g. database) daripada terubah/terpadam masa stack UPDATE вҖ” beza dengan DeletionPolicy (yang protect masa stack DELETE). Exam: "prevent accidental updates to specific resources during a stack update" вҶ’ Stack Policy.',
              'Termination Protection: setting di STACK level yang halang stack itu sendiri daripada dipadam (mesti disable dulu sebelum boleh delete). BEZA: Termination Protection = halang stack DELETE; DeletionPolicy: Retain = kalau stack memang dipadam, kekalkan resource tertentu. Exam: "prevent the stack from being deleted" вҶ’ Termination Protection; "keep the database if the stack is deleted" вҶ’ DeletionPolicy: Retain.',
