            sifir: ["Relational + transaksi OLTP вҶ’ RDS (standard) / Aurora (HA hebat, auto-scale).", "Key-value, ms latency, serverless, spiky вҶ’ DynamoDB. Microsecond atas DynamoDB вҶ’ +DAX.", "MongoDB вҶ’ DocumentDB. Cassandra вҶ’ Keyspaces. Graph/relationship/fraud вҶ’ Neptune.", "Analytics/warehouse/aggregate berjuta baris (OLAP) вҶ’ Redshift. Time-series/IoT вҶ’ Timestream.", "Cache depan SEBARANG DB вҶ’ ElastiCache (Redis/Memcached).", "Trap: OLTP (checkout/transaksi) = RDS/Aurora; OLAP (laporan/dashboard) = Redshift.", "RDS = 6 enjin RELATIONAL je (MySQL, PostgreSQL, MariaDB, Oracle, SQL Server, Aurora). NoSQL/cache/warehouse/graph/time-series = BUKAN RDS.", "Server-based = bayar instance 24/7 walau idle (RDS biasa, Aurora biasa). Serverless = bayar guna je / scale near-zero (DynamoDB, Keyspaces, Aurora Serverless v2).", "'Aurora' вү  serverless melainkan ada perkataan 'Serverless' di belakang. Aurora biasa = server-based cluster."],
            perangkap: [{"soalan": "App perlu cari semua mutual friends & detect fraud ring dalam data berhubung-rapat (highly connected). Database?", "umpan": "DynamoDB вҖ” sebab dia laju & scalable, ramai default pilih untuk apa-apa NoSQL.", "betul": "Neptune вҖ” keyword 'relationship / mutual friends / fraud ring / connected data' = graph = Neptune. DynamoDB key-value, teruk untuk traverse relationship."}, {"soalan": "Aplikasi e-commerce transaksi (checkout, tolak stok, simpan order) perlukan consistency kuat & SQL. Database?", "umpan": "Redshift вҖ” sebab dia handle data besar & SQL, nampak macam boleh.", "betul": "RDS/Aurora вҖ” keyword 'transaksi / checkout / OLTP' = relational OLTP = RDS/Aurora. Redshift = OLAP/analytics (aggregate), teruk untuk single-row insert/update."}, {"soalan": "App relational MySQL dengan traffic ON-OFF teruk (dev-test waktu office je, malam sunyi). Nak bayar ikut guna & scale near-zero bila idle. Pilih?", "umpan": "Amazon RDS MySQL (Multi-AZ) вҖ” sebab 'relational MySQL' terus pilih RDS biasa. SALAH: RDS biasa server-based, bayar instance 24/7 walau idle вҖ” bukan 'pay per use / scale to zero'.", "betul": "Aurora Serverless v2 вҖ” keyword 'unpredictable/intermittent/dev-test + scale near-zero + pay per use' = serverless. 'Aurora' je вү  serverless; mesti ada 'Serverless' di belakang nama."}, {"soalan": "Nak simpan shopping cart / user session berskala besar, schemaless, latency millisecond. Database?", "umpan": "Amazon RDS вҖ” sebab 'database' biasa orang fikir SQL/RDS dulu. SALAH: cart/session = key-value schemaless, RDS (relational, fixed schema) leceh & susah scale.", "betul": "DynamoDB вҖ” keyword 'session / shopping cart / schemaless / any scale / single-digit ms' = key-value NoSQL = DynamoDB (BUKAN RDS вҖ” DynamoDB bukan bawah RDS langsung)."}],
