              'Umpan paling biasa: RDS (boleh JOIN) atau DynamoDB (NoSQL default). Discriminator = "hubungan dalam / berlapis". RDS JOIN bersarang = lambat; DynamoDB tak boleh traverse. Hubungan dalam вҶ’ Neptune.',
              'PRICING: instance-based. db.t3.medium ~$0.0832/hr (dev), db.r5.large ~$0.348/hr (prod) us-east-1. Storage $0.10/GB-bulan, I/O $0.20 per 1 juta request, backup $0.021/GB-bulan. Neptune Serverless ~$0.1608 per NCU-jam (auto-scale untuk beban naik-turun). Takde free tier.',
              'PRICING discriminator: beban graph stabil вҶ’ instance provisioned (murah/jam). Beban naik-turun / spiky / dev вҶ’ Neptune Serverless (bayar ikut NCU, tak idle-charge sebanyak instance penuh).',
