            scenario: '"Durable in-memory database as a primary store, microsecond reads, no separate backing DB" вҶ’ Amazon MemoryDB. "In-memory CACHE in front of an existing DB (data boleh hilang)" вҶ’ ElastiCache (atau DAX khusus DynamoDB). Keywords: durable in-memory, Redis/Valkey primary database, Multi-AZ transactional log.',
            detailsLabel: 'Anatomy MemoryDB',
            storageDetails: 'In-memory data store вҶ’ semua data dalam RAM вҶ’ microsecond reads, single-digit ms writes. Valkey/Redis OSS commands.\nMulti-AZ transactional log вҶ’ INI yang bagi durability: setiap write ditulis ke log merentas berbilang AZ SEBELUM di-ack. Node mati вҶ’ data tak hilang, failover pulih dari log.\nCluster + shards вҶ’ data dipecah ikut shard (horizontal scale); tiap shard ada primary + replica untuk HA.\nSnapshots вҶ’ backup ke S3 untuk restore / point-in-time.',
