            perangkap: [{"soalan": "App perlu extract data berstruktur (nama, jumlah, tarikh) dari ribuan invois scan PDF. Servis mana?", "umpan": "Amazon Rekognition вҖ” orang ingat 'analisa imej jadi Rekognition', tapi Rekognition untuk muka/objek/scene, bukan baca teks/borang/jadual dari dokumen.", "betul": "Amazon Textract вҖ” OCR khas untuk extract teks, forms, tables dari dokumen. Keyword: 'OCR', 'scanned PDF', 'forms/tables', 'invoice'."}, {"soalan": "Bina pipeline: terima audio meeting bahasa Jepun вҶ’ simpan transkrip Inggeris вҶ’ analisa sentiment. Servis mana ikut turutan?", "umpan": "Guna satu servis je macam Comprehend untuk semua вҖ” Comprehend NLP sahaja, tak boleh transkrip audio atau translate.", "betul": "Transcribe (audioвҶ’teks) вҶ’ Translate (JPвҶ’EN) вҶ’ Comprehend (sentiment). Setiap langkah satu pre-built API. Keyword: 'transcribe + translate + sentiment pipeline'."}],
            storageDetails: 'Amazon Polly вҶ’ Text-to-Speech (TTS): convert text jadi audio (natural voice)\nAmazon Transcribe вҶ’ Speech-to-Text (STT): convert audio/video jadi text\nAmazon Lex вҶ’ Conversational chatbot: NLU + ASR, maintains context, integrates Lambda (powers Alexa)\nAmazon Rekognition вҶ’ Image/Video analysis: face detection, object/scene detection, labels\nAmazon Comprehend вҶ’ NLP: sentiment analysis, entities, key phrases, language detection\nAmazon Textract вҶ’ Document OCR: extract text, forms, tables from PDFs/images\nAmazon Translate вҶ’ Neural machine translation: convert text between languages, real-time + batch\nKinesis Video Streams вҶ’ Ingest, store, process video/audio streams (for Rekognition real-time analysis)',
